es a crackling sound."}, {"version": "white", "text": "Using electricity stored in its fur, it stimulates its muscles to heighten its reaction speed."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "Using electricity stored in its fur, it stimulates its muscles to heighten its reaction speed."}, {"version": "x", "text": "Using electricity stored in its fur, it stimulates its muscles to heighten its reaction speed."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It stores static electricity in its fur for discharging. It gives off sparks if a storm approaches."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "diamond", "emerald", "firered", "heartgold", "leafgreen", "omega-ruby", "pearl", "platinum", "ruby", "sapphire", "shield", "soulsilver", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "brilliant-diamond-shining-pearl", "colosseum", "diamond-pearl", "emerald", "firered-leafgreen", "heartgold-soulsilver", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "platinum", "ruby-sapphire", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y", "xd"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "electrike"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "manectric"}]}